   <body>
      <p>
         <ul id="ul_mvv_lyr_wgc">
            <li>Hydraulic oil + Additives (Limited slip)<note type="note" id="note_nvv_lyr_wgc">
                  <p>Use an oil with an appropriate viscosity rate considering the ambient
                            temperature to avoid oil leakage and cooler damages.</p>
               </note>
            </li>
            <li>Normal temperature: ISO VG22-32</li>
            <li>Ultra low temperature: ISO VG15</li>
            <li>Ultra high temperature: ISO VG46</li>
         </ul>
      </p>
      <p>Oils should have antiwear, antifoam, antirust and antioxidation additives for heavy duty
            use as stated by the oil supplier. ISO viscosity grade of 32 would normally be
            selected.</p>
      <p>Use the oil below as the additive to brake oil:</p>
      <p>
         <ul id="ul_ovv_lyr_wgc">
            <li>Lubrizol LZ 9990A</li>
         </ul>
      </p>
